{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInputStreamSignalName"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInputStreamSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO25FileInputStreamSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Case","title":"FileInputStreamSignalName.notify","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/fileinputstreamsignalname\/notify"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Fi